Commentary Text: Chahal to Rayudu, out Caught by Padikkal!! Another one bites the dust and CSK are imploding here after the platform Moeen gave them with the powerplay! The surface is clearly assisting spin and Chahal bowls a lovely leg break that spins across Rayudu. Lunges forward in hope and just has a tentative poke at this one, edging it low to first slip. The umps wanted to be doubly sure about the catch, although everyone else including Rayudu were sure about it. The momentum has clearly shifted now in RR's favour. Rayudu c Padikkal b Chahal 3(6)
